:INFO
AI Video Editing for Solo Creators
Descript, Runway, and CapCut offer AI-powered editing features that cut production time significantly. The key is a structured workflow that uses each tool for what it does best.

:COUNTER.half
60% Faster
Rough cut time with AI-assisted transcription editing
|
:COUNTER.half
Under 50 USD
Monthly cost for a full AI video editing stack

:PATH
Organize Phase
Import all footage. Use AI transcription in Descript to generate a script from your recording. Label and color-code clips by topic.

:PATH
Cut Phase
Edit using the transcript in Descript. Delete filler words automatically. Export a rough cut timeline to your primary editor.

:PATH
Enhance Phase
Use Runway for background removal, object cleanup, or short AI-generated B-roll inserts. Export final cut at target resolution.

:CHECKLIST
Video Editing Workflow Checklist
[ ] Import and organize all raw footage
[ ] Generate transcript with Descript
[ ] Remove filler words and long pauses
[ ] Export rough cut
[ ] Add B-roll and graphics
[ ] Apply color grade
[ ] Mix audio levels
[ ] Export and upload

:NOTE
Descript's Overdub feature lets you fix spoken mistakes by typing. This eliminates re-recording short corrections and saves significant studio time for talking-head content.

